rows.label: qst103108_msg0001
rows.name:
Hmm? You look rather pleased.
Did something good happen?

rows.label: qst103108_msg0003
rows.name:
The pattern engraved on it is the same
as the murals, from the ancient Nopon
tribe... This is a great discovery!

rows.label: qst103108_msg0004
rows.name:
However, we don't know
where the keyhole is.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0005
rows.name:
It is better for you, as travelers,
to hold onto it rather than I.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0006
rows.name:
I pray that you will find
a keyhole that fits.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0007
rows.name:
As for me... I'm not keen
on returning to Superbia.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0008
rows.name:
I shall remain in this village and
study the murals in greater depth.

rows.label: qst103108_msg0009
rows.name:
You have been a great
help to me. I thank you.
